Okay, so I'm convinced - after reading about this card game for years now!
But, Amazon no longer carries it and their link to the company that does
(carefreeproducts.com) says they are out of stock. We're going on a trip, my
kids and a few other teens, and I thought it would be great to have a new
game.
Anyone know where I could find it?
Thanks and aloha,
